name: Captain Cod
description:
Behind the rugged beard and thousand yard stare lies a man who loves the simple things in life such as telling wildly exaggerated stories, singing sea shanty’s, and of course, holding doors open.

  • Each Wedgie is individually hand painted.
  • Each Wedgie has their name/description printed on the reverse.
  • Dimensions: W 4cm x L 23cm x H 3cm.
  • All orders are shipped direct from our UK office and are sealed in a jiffy bag.

name: Macka
description:
After being kicked out of the local tennis league for one too many umpire 'debates', Macka has now taken up the noble art of professional door stopping. Although he's calmed down in his later years; he still relishes the challenge of arguing with any troublesome doors that refuse to be held in place. His passion is unmatched but a word of warning, he is always right.

  • Each Wedgie is individually hand painted.
  • Each Wedgie has their name/description printed on the reverse.
  • Dimensions: W 4cm x L 23cm x H 3cm.
  • All orders are shipped direct from our UK office and are sealed in a jiffy bag.

name: Nick
description:
Nick is constantly ducking out of his responsibilities to nip down the back nine. He tells us he’s the hit of the nineteenth hole due to his repertoire of ‘old golfers never die, they just....’ jokes. We think he should concentrate on doing his job.
